  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "2. Slice the French bread into 1-inch thick slices and toast until lightly browned.",
    "3. In a large bowl, combine roasted eggplant, diced tomato, and halved cherry tomatoes.",
    "4. In a small bowl, whisk together Thai red chili sauce and a pinch of salt.",
    "5. Brush the toasted bread slices with coconut oil and top with the eggplant mixture.",
    "6. Drizzle the chili sauce mixture over the top and garnish with chopped cilantro.",
    "7. Season with salt to taste and serve immediately."
  ],
